org.apache.calcite.sql.util

类 SqlBasicVisitor<R>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.calcite.sql.util.SqlBasicVisitor<R>
  • 类型参数:
    R - Return type
    所有已实现的接口:
    SqlVisitor<R>
    直接已知子类:
    SqlShuttle, Util.OverFinder

    public class SqlBasicVisitor<R>
extends Object
implements SqlVisitor<R>
    Basic implementation of SqlVisitor which does nothing at each node.

    This class is useful as a base class for classes which implement the SqlVisitor interface. The derived class can override whichever methods it chooses.

    • 嵌套类概要

      Argument handler.
      static class  SqlBasicVisitor.ArgHandlerImpl<R>
      Default implementation of SqlBasicVisitor.ArgHandler which merely calls SqlNode.accept(org.apache.calcite.sql.util.SqlVisitor<R>) on each operand.
